    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for someone prioritizing function over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the roof, and a few scuffs on the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though it may require some routine maintenance and suspension work in the near future to keep it at its best. It is a solid, honest car for a buyer looking for a budget-friendly daily driver.",
