    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a parts car or for someone looking for an extensive restoration project. The exterior has significant rust, major paint failure, and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and cracked plastics. Mechanically, it requires immediate attention as it currently has difficulty starting and several major components are nearing the end of their lifespan. Please expect a vehicle that needs significant work before it can be considered roadworthy.",
